{
  "stem": "10496.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- but Hitler had made a decision in-- in October, 1940.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said that-- there were about 180,000 Jews left in Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said, I don't want them there anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm going-- I'm going-- I'm going out to war, you see, so I'm going-- I can't have a fifth column.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Somebody-- I can't have the Jews to mess up-- mess up my--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right-- 1938, right after-- after November 10, 1938.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, November 10.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they stayed there for about three months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he told me, though, that there were-- not only-- there were Jews, but there were others as well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Dissenters, communists, or anyone who didn't like Hitler's way of governing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, after-- when he came back from Dachau, he realized that Hitler meant business.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, no one was safe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, no one, Jews or gypsy or dissenters, communist, whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] so the die was cast.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She went through Sweden.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, she-- I-- I guess she took the train to-- to the north of Germany, and then across to Sweden.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I definitely-- I was crying and she was crying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was just a-- a-- a traumatic experience.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Traumatic.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it had to happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'll tell you the truth, it was a good thing it did happen because later on, eventually-- as we were-- we were in southern France, she was able to-- to keep in touch with us all the time, and HIAS also helped a great deal.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "HIAS, H-I-A-S, Hebrew Immigration, something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- they were very active in--in trying to save Jew-- Jewish people, and--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "New York.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
